00:10:25.290 --> 00:10:29.740
can relate to, programmers
aren't just programmers.

00:10:29.740 --> 00:10:33.730
They have a wonderful
sense of the world,

00:10:33.730 --> 00:10:35.180
of the philosophical challenges.

00:10:38.028 --> 00:10:40.860
