to sort of describe

00:10:40.860 --> 00:10:42.760
what Anwar is up
against, and what

00:10:42.760 --> 00:10:46.630
is beginning to change his
life, that sort of influences

00:10:46.630 --> 00:10:47.590
the conversation.

00:10:47.590 --> 00:10:49.670
So the coding then
begins to take

00:10:49.670 --> 00:10:52.840
