is more than just functional,

00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:54.550
it can have a symbolic value.

00:10:54.550 --> 00:10:56.660
So even if we're
commenting out something,

00:10:56.660 --> 00:11:00.360
those things can
not only resonate

00:11:00.360 --> 00:11:04.270
on a sort of a literary
level, but they can also

00:11:04.270 --> 00:11:13.160
contain obscure codes that
need to be sort of rendered

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:14.220
in a different way.

00:11:14.220 --> 00:11:18.040
And if they are, if they
are looked at with that eye,

00:11:18.040 --> 00:11:19.490
they can reveal more things.

00:11:19.490 --> 00:11:22.337
Not only about the code,
but about the story itself.

00:11:22.337 --> 00:11:24.920
